{{template "layout" .}}

{{define "title"}}player profile - {{$.Site.Brand.Brand}}{{end}}

{{define "content"}}
<main class="lancer-page lancer-profile">
  <header class="lancer-page-hero profile-hero cinematic-stage runway-stage about-stage page-opening" style="--opening-image:url('/static/media/interests/verstappen-user.jpg'); --opening-position:68% 35%">
    <div class="cinematic-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="page-poster-word" aria-hidden="true">PROFILE</div>
    <div class="page-hero-copy reveal">
      <div class="lancer-kicker"><span>PLAYER PROFILE</span><i></i><span>CALLSIGN / LANCER</span></div>
      <p class="page-command"><span>lancer@field-notes:~$</span> cat ./identity/profile.manifest</p>
      <h1>{{if .About.TitleAccent}}{{SplitAccent .About.Title .About.TitleAccent}}{{else}}{{RenderInline .About.Title}}{{end}}</h1>
      <div class="profile-intro">{{range .About.Intro}}<p>{{.}}</p>{{end}}</div>
      <div class="profile-meta">
        {{range .About.Meta}}<div><span>{{.K}}</span><strong>{{.V}}</strong></div>{{end}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="profile-card dev-manifest reveal">
      <div class="dev-editor-head"><span><i></i><i></i><i></i></span><strong>profile.manifest</strong><b>READ ONLY</b></div>
      <div class="manifest-code">
        <p><i>01</i><span>callsign</span> = <b>"Lancer"</b></p>
        <p><i>02</i><span>role</span> = <b>"programmer"</b></p>
        <p><i>03</i><span>stack.current</span> = [</p>
        <p><i>04</i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>"frontend"</em>, <em>"go"</em>, <em>"agents"</em></p>
        <p><i>05</i>]</p>
        <p><i>06</i><span>mental</span> = <strong>hold_the_clutch</strong></p>
        <p><i>07</i><span>privacy</span> = <strong>true</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="manifest-status"><span>PROCESS</span><strong>ROUND_ACTIVE</strong><i></i></div>
    </aside>
    <a class="drawer-cue" href="#about-drawer" data-drawer-target="about-drawer" aria-label="继续向下浏览">
      <span>SCROLL TO OPEN</span><b aria-hidden="true">↓</b>
    </a>
  </header>
  <div class="page-drawer" id="about-drawer">
    <button class="drawer-handle" type="button" data-drawer-handle aria-label="按住拖动打开页面内容，或点击继续浏览"><span aria-hidden="true"></span></button>
  <section class="profile-lanes">
    <article class="profile-lane on-track reveal">
      <div class="lane-label"><span>01</span><strong>ON TRACK</strong></div>
      <h2>把问题拆开，把今天推进一点。</h2>
      <p>技术是我的赛道。前端、Go、Agent 和后端不是简历标签，而是一圈一圈跑出来的判断力。</p>
      <div class="lane-route" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
    </article>
    <article class="profile-lane off-track reveal">
      <div class="lane-label"><span>02</span><strong>OFF TRACK</strong></div>
      <h2>热爱不是休息区，它是继续进攻的燃料。</h2>
      <p>比赛、音乐和那些传奇时刻，让不顺利的日子仍然保留一点期待。</p>
      <div class="lane-signal">PADDOCK / COURT / SERVER / PLAYLIST</div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="influence-board interactive-influences" data-active="f1" aria-labelledby="profile-influences">
    <div class="lancer-section-head reveal">
      <div class="lancer-section-index"><span>03</span><p>INFLUENCES</p></div>
      <div><h2 id="profile-influences">把鼠标放上去。每一种热爱，都在训练同一个我。</h2></div>
    </div>
    <div class="influence-interactive-shell reveal">
      <aside class="influence-preview" aria-live="polite">
        <div class="influence-preview-media" aria-hidden="true">
          <i class="influence-preview-image is-active" style="--influence-image:url('/static/media/interests/verstappen-user.jpg')"></i><i class="influence-preview-image"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="influence-preview-top"><span>influence.current</span><b>POINTER / FOCUS</b></div>
        <div class="influence-preview-code"><i>const</i> drive = <strong>resolve(activeInfluence)</strong>;</div>
        <div class="influence-preview-copy">
          <span id="influence-preview-index">01 / PADDOCK</span>
          <h3 id="influence-preview-title">VERSTAPPEN / LECLERC</h3>
          <p id="influence-preview-copy">速度、进攻、精密，以及下一圈仍然敢于压上。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="influence-preview-line"><i></i><span>INPUT DETECTED</span></div>
      </aside>
      <div class="influence-board-grid" role="group" aria-label="Lancer influences">
        <button type="button" class="influence-board-card" data-influence="f1" data-image="/static/media/interests/verstappen-user.jpg" data-position="62% 32%" data-index="01 / PADDOCK" aria-pressed="true">
          <span>F1 / 01</span><h3>VERSTAPPEN / LECLERC</h3><p>速度、进攻、精密，以及下一圈仍然敢于压上。</p><b>↗</b>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="influence-board-card" data-influence="sport" data-image="/static/media/interests/curry-new-user.jpg" data-position="50% 58%" data-size="cover" data-index="02 / COURT + PITCH" aria-pressed="false">
          <span>SPORT / 02</span><h3>CURRY / MESSI</h3><p>把千万次训练藏进本能，在看似没有空间的位置完成突破。</p><b>↗</b>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="influence-board-card" data-influence="server" data-image="/static/media/interests/niko-user.jpg" data-position="66% 24%" data-index="03 / SERVER" aria-pressed="false">
          <span>SERVER / 03</span><h3>NiKo / TheShy</h3><p>十年饮冰，难凉热血。进入战场时敢于撕开第一道防线。</p><b>↗</b>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="influence-board-card" data-influence="music" data-image="/static/media/interests/gem-user.jpg" data-position="50% 42%" data-size="cover" data-index="04 / SOUNDTRACK" aria-pressed="false">
          <span>MIX / 04</span><h3>MANDOPOP / PHONK / EDM</h3><p>周杰伦、邓紫棋与新的节拍，组成每一个高光时刻的声音。</p><b>↗</b>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="profile-story reveal">
    <div class="story-label"><span>04</span><p>LONG FORM</p></div>
    <div class="about-body lancer-about-body">
      {{if .About.BodyMarkdown}}{{.About.BodyHTML}}{{else}}<h2>关于这个博客</h2><p>这里记录每一次探索、失误、修正和继续向前。</p>{{end}}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="current-round reveal">
    <div class="current-round-head"><span>CURRENT ROUND</span><strong>LIVE</strong></div>
    <div class="current-round-grid">
      <div><p>NOW PLAYING</p><h2>还在学习，<br>还在进攻。</h2></div>
      <div class="now-term lancer-now-term">
        <div class="head"><span class="name">lancer@field-notes / now.txt</span></div>
        <div class="body">
          {{range $l := .Now.Lines}}
          {{if $l.IsCmd}}<div class="ln"><span class="p">$</span> {{if $l.F}}<span class="f">{{$l.F}}</span> {{end}}{{$l.Args}}{{if $l.C}} <span class="c">{{$l.C}}</span>{{end}}</div>{{end}}
          {{if not $l.IsCmd}}<div class="ln">{{$l.Arrow}} <span class="k">{{$l.K}}</span>{{if $l.IsString}} <span class="s">{{$l.V}}</span>{{else}} <span class="v">{{$l.V}}</span>{{end}}</div>{{end}}
          {{end}}
          <div class="ln"><span class="p">$</span> <span class="c">_</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</main>
{{end}}